ise\" class=\"card__icon\" aria-label=\"Instagram\">\n                    <i class=\"fab fa-instagram\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>\n                  </a>\n                  \n                  <a href=\"https://twitch.tv/colecaccamise\" class=\"card__icon\" aria-label=\"Twitch\">\n                  <i class=\"fab fa-twitch\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>\n                    </a>\n\n                </div>\n\n                <h3>Content Creator</h3>\n                <p class=\"card__description\">\n                  I make videos and take photos of tech produtcts I love using.\n                </p>\n                <p class=\"card__description\">\n                 I go for a cinematic sort of style, and am always improving the quality of what I put out.\n                </p>\n                <p class=\"card__description\">\n                  Follow me to watch my journey\n                 </p>\n                <a href=\"http://kit.co/colecaccamise\" class=\"card__cta\">My Gear & Equipment -></a>\n              </div>\n              \n              <div class=\"card\">\n                <div class=\"card__icons\">\n                  <a href=\"https://github.com/colecaccamise\" class=\"card__icon\" aria-label=\"GitHub\">\n                    <i class=\"fab fa-github\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>\n                    </a>\n                    <a href=\"portfolio\" class=\"card__icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\">              \n                      <i class=\"fas fa-laptop-code\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>\n                      </a>\n                </div>\n\n\n                <h3>Web Developer</h3>\n                  <p class=\"card__description\">\n                    I'm a self-taught web developer. I enjoy working on the front-end most, and recently I've been brushing up on my skills in JavaScript and CSS.\n                  </p>\n\n                  <div class=\"card__list-container\">\n                    <div>\n                      <h4 class=\"card__subheading\">Languages</h